metadata.name: the mfkng judgment (2022)
metadata.description:
Inspired by the Italian Renaissance Michelangelo's fresco, 'the mfkng judgment' is a digital depiction of the First Coming of Sartoshi and the final and eternal meme judgment by God of all NFTs.
The meme rise and descend to their fates, while Sartoshi reigns in center surrounded by prominent OG Mfers. Altogether there are over 300 figures, with nearly all the OG mfers, few of them have been covered up by mfers derivatives and external CC0 belowed projects, that still remain intact after recent cleaning and restoration.
